ing behavior can appear or disappear on the\nintersection and describe what consequences this has on the dynamics on the\nadjacent codimension-1 discontinuity sets. Finally, we show the existence of\ncanard explosions of regularizations of PWS systems in $\\mathbb R^3$ that\ndepend on a single unfolding parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Sep 2019 11:17:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-24"}
